title: Check out this 3 bed in South Austin
posting_body: While maintaining a focus on comfort, this floor plan gives you the options you want.
Bathrooms that include Roman-style tub & dual-sink vanities.
The details and features that come standard are sure to please.
Your gourmet kitchen comes equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a tile backsplash.
Track lighting and wood-style flooring create a modern yet inviting atmosphere.
You’ll also love the additional space afforded by the walk-in closets and private patio.
Short commute to downtown & the airport.
Get it quick before this bridge of opportunity burns!
Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor
*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.
